Class DrivebaseS

  • java.lang.Object
    • frc.robot.subsystems.DrivebaseS
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.Subsystem
    public class DrivebaseS
extends java.lang.Object
implements edu.wpi.first.wpilibj2.command.Subsystem
    This subsystem is for the drivetrain, which is made up of two master Talons and two sets of Victors, each on a side of the drivetrain.
